Technical function / Advisory, training and coaching services to members
OSID / FO has solid and representative local membership base (‘representativeness’)
OSID / FO’s governance is transparent, accountable and according to democratic principles (‘accountability’)
OSID / FO has systems in place, which facilitate member involvement in strategy setting and monitoring and in decisions (‘participation’)
OSID / FO has improved the capacity to adapt its member services in changing markets and functioning environment (‘integrated services’)
OSID / FO implements policies to empower young people, women and specific groups (‘inclusiveness’)
